summary: This document is an invoice from FedEx for shipping services provided to NYSG LLC. It details the charges incurred for transportation and special handling, along with the billing and shipping addresses.
keyFacts: Total charges on the invoice amount to USD 5.50.
The shipping address is listed as NYSG LLC, 457 Madison Ave, New York, NY.
The package was picked up on August 1, 2003, and delivered on August 4, 2003.
